  "texts": [
    "User interactions, including manual rephrasings are logged for further fine-tuning.",
    "To balance between access to external LLMs and the potential risk of enterprise data leakage, we proposed the QueryShield platform.",
    "It lies between any external LLM and the enterprise environment and detects sensitive data leakage in the queries as well as rephrases the original queries to remove any potential data leakage.",
    "We explored multiple lightweight language models as part of QueryShield so that they can be hosted in-house with limited hardware resources.",
    "We evaluated these models for the tasks of detecting sensitive data leakage, rephrasing sensitive queries, and identifying data leakage types, using a manually annotated dataset of 1500 queries."
  ],
